Name:           lib%{libname}
Version:        0.7.20
Release:        1%{?dist}
Epoch:          1
Summary:        Package dependency solver

License:        BSD
URL:            https://github.com/openSUSE/libsolv
%if %{defined commit}
Source:         %{url}/archive/%{commit}/%{name}-%{shortcommit}.tar.gz
%else
